window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Are you looking to expand your knowledge to completely random, utterly thought-provoking, thoroughly funny anecdotes?</b></p> <p><b>Would you like to initiate the most stimulating conversations of the evening with mind-blowing stories?</b></p> <p>With <i>The Big Fat Book of Interesting Stories, </i>you will always have at your disposal fun facts and trivia to tease your mind and amaze your friends and family!</p> <p>Sink to the depths of the ocean with Violet Jessop, dance in the ballet that caused a riot, and fly away in a lawn chair! Stories have the power to transport us to places and times unknown: These stories will bring you to the craziest times in history and the silliest places on Earth.</p> <p>This is not just a compilation of dry facts; the funny and tragical, heart-melting and mind-boggling stories in this book are written with great care to details, historical context, and most importantly terrible puns!</p> <p><b>Just a few things you will discover in this book:</b></p> <p></p> <ul> <li>The funniest and most terrible little-known facts of history</li> <li>Why London stank so bad in 1858</li> <li>How a baboon ran a railway</li> <li>How a fashion craze was born out of tar</li> <li>Contemporary nuggets: unbelievable stories that are unfolding right now!</li> <li>Why you can’t escape paying taxes (even during a zombie apocalypse!)</li> <li>Discover the country that you can rent on Airbnb</li> <li>The stories of heroes and villains forgotten by history</li> <li>The exciting life of a pirate queen</li> <li>The silly tales behind great (and not so great) discoveries</li> <li>How a bagel won a war&nbsp;</li> <li>The spy story behind the creepiest doll</li> <li>The gripping adventures of the men and women who survived the most harrowing conditions</li> <li>How to survive a plane crash and a sinking boat</li> <li>And much much more!</li> </ul> <p>Satisfy your most unquenchable thirst for completely useless, yet totally funny tales of adventures, misfortunes, and happy accidents!&nbsp;</p> <p>What are you waiting for?</p> <p><b>Get a copy of </b><b><i>The Big Fat Book of Interesting Stories</i></b><b> and get ready for the wildest, oddest, funniest stories about science, history, food, animals, and much more!</b></p>"; 
